@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Medicine and Dietary Supplements Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to our website. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit and use our medicine and dietary supplements store.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>We collect personal information that you provide when you register an account, place an order, or interact with our website. This information may include your name, email address, shipping address, phone number, and payment details.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use your personal information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Process orders and provide customer service.</li>
                <li>Improve your user experience and our website.</li>
                <li>Send notifications about products, promotions, and important information related to our services.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Information Security</h2>
            <p>We are committed to protecting your personal information by implementing appropriate security measures. However, no security system is impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Sharing Information with Third Parties</h2>
            <p>We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to process orders, comply with legal obligations, or with your consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal information. To exercise these rights, please contact us using the contact information provided on our website.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page. Please review it periodically to stay informed of any updates.</p>
        </div>


</body>
</html>
